  <brief_title>Debulking Effect of Curretage on Basal Cell Carcinomas - a Histological Assessment.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Relation of Basal Cell Carcinoma Tumour Thickness, Histologically Estimated, in Punch Biopsies Performed Before and After Curretage.</official_title>
