  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study was to compare histologically observed tumour infitration of basal cell
      carcinoma (bcc) lesions before and after curretage.A significant reduction of tumour depth
      would enable further bcc's included for superficial non-invasive treatment modalities such as
      topical photodynamic therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
